v class=\"current wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n<div class=\"clearfix container\">\n    <div class=\"pull-left banner-tt\">\n\n\n\n流体力学研究所</div>\n    <div class=\"pull-left nav-b\">                <a href=\"../../index.htm\">首页</a>\n                &gt;\n                <a href=\"../../szqk.htm\">师资情况</a>\n                &gt;\n                <a href=\"../../szqk/szxx.htm\">师资信息</a>\n                &gt;\n                <a href=\"../../szqk/szxx/gclxx.htm\">工程力学系</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"clearfix container\"><ul class=\"pull-right banner-ul clearfix\">\n    \n    <li><a href=\"../../szqk/ys.htm\" title=\"院士\">院士</a></li>\n\n    \n    <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"../../szqk/szxx.htm\" title=\"师资信息\">师资信息</a></li>\n\n</ul></div>\n</div>\n  </div>\n\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n<div>\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/engine.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js\"></script><link href=\"/system/resource/style/component/news/content/format2.css\" type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><form name=\"_newscontent_fromname\">\n\n<div style=\"background: #fff;\">\n\n       <div class=\"teach-top wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: visible; animation-name: fadeInUp;\">\n            <div class=\"teach-top-img\"><img src=\"/__local/7/6B/C0/6BB84540B2037A972129DC8B3BC_07529388_74EB2.jpg\"></div>\n            <div class=\"teacher-name\"><a>牛洪涛</a></div>\n            <div class=\"teacher-p\">\n                <div class=\"row\">\n                    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\n                                  \n                                  \n                                  \n                    </div>\n                    \n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div> \n        <div id=\"vsb_content_2\"><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">个人简介</div><div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">牛洪涛，清华大学航天航空学院，高级工程师</p>\n</div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">教育背景</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">1990/09-1995/06，清华大学，精密仪器与机械系，本科，导师：刘成颖</p>\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">2005/05-2008/06，中国矿业大学，机电学院，硕士，导师：余震危</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">参与科研项目</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">2020-08至今，风洞融合数字化教学实验平台建设，265万，在研，主持。</p>\n<p>2018-06至2021-06 《实验科学与技术》课程建设----小风洞速压采集系统设计与制造， 8万，主持，完成。</p>\n<p>2018-07至2018-09 院级改善办学条件项目----直流式水洞重建， 30万，主持，完成。</p>\n<p>2016-09至2018-09，校级研究生教改项目----电子压力扫描系统升级改造， 20万，主持，完成。</p>\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">2008-01至-2010-12， 某型飞行器气动问题研究（863项目），240万，参加，完成。</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">期刊论文</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">(1)<strong>牛洪涛</strong>、王连泽、沈熊;激光多普勒测速仪产品研发与应用，实验技术与管理，2015年/3，101-105</p>\n<p><b>(2)</b><b>牛洪涛</b>，李治明，沈熊; 应用LDV测量水洞式游泳机波浪水流速度特性，实验技术与管理，2018，35(9)，55-58</p>\n<p>(3) Peng J, Zhang Z Y, <b>Niu H T</b>;A three-dimensional two-phase model for a membraneless fuel cell using decomposition of hydrogen peroxide with Yshaped Microchannel. Fuel Cells, 2012, 12 (6), 1009-1018.</p>\n<p>(4)Lian-Ze Wang*, <b>Hong-Tao Niu</b>, Ning-Ning Peng, Xiong Shen</p>\n<p>Research into Haze Removal Method Based on Diffusion and Relative Motion Aerosol and Air Quality Research, 2016，16: 1757–1763</p>\n<p>(5)Tian Z W, <b>Niu H T</b>, Wu Z N. Flow past polygons with an odd number of edges, SCIENCE CHINA-PHYSICS MECHANICS &amp; ASTRONOMY, 2011, 54(4), 683-689.</p>\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">(6)韩标，<b>牛洪涛</b>;竖直平板间湍流自然对流中螺旋羽流结构的实验研究，实验流体力学，2011，25(6), 13-18。</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">会议论文</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">(1) Wang Bing,<b> Niu Hongtao</b>, Lu Hao, Zhang Huiqiang1, Wang Xilin;</p>\n<p>FLOW VISUALIZATION OF INTERACTIONS BETWEEN PARTICLE WAKES AND JET VORTICES,FLUCOME 2009,Moscow,Russia,2009-8-17至2009-8-21<b> </b></p>\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">(2) 田中伟，<b>牛洪涛</b>，孙涤清，吴知非，周睿，吴子牛；临近空间新概念思考,临近空间飞行器创新研讨会，2008，长沙，2018.07.11—07.14。</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">获奖</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">牛洪涛（1/3）多功能模块式激光多普勒测速实验台，全国第四届高等学校自制实验教学仪器设备评选，全国高等教育学会，二等奖，2016，（牛洪涛，王连泽，沈熊）</p>\n<p>牛洪涛（1/1），清华大学学生实验室建设指导奖---教学风洞设计与制造，清华大学设备处，一等奖， 2018，（牛洪涛）</p>\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">2019年获得第十二届（2017-2018年）“清华大学优秀实验技术人员”</p></div></div>\n\n     </div>\n</form>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"footer wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"friends-box wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n        <div class=\"friends-left\">友情链接</div>\n    <a href=\"https://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1696534067, 71220)\">清华大学</a>\n\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"clearfix wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n        <div class=\"pull-left footer-logo\">                            <img src=\"../../images/logo.png\">\n</div>\n        <div class=\"pull-right footer-txt\"><!-- 版权内容请在本组件\"内容配置-版权\"处填写 -->\n<p>版权所有 © 清华大学京ICP备15006448号 京公网安备 110402430053 号&nbsp;</p><p>推荐ie8以上谷歌等浏览器浏览网页<